4 ways to create a thread :
    1. extending a thread class
    2. extends the runnable interface
    3. implements the runnable interface as anonymous class
    4. implements the runnable interface as lambda expression

* Jvm will stay alive as long as there are any remaining thread running even if Main thread has terminated ( example 8) { if don't want this behavior mark them as
    deamon thread}
* it is also possible for one thread to wait for another thread to terminate